15
00:00:54.040 --> 00:00:57.340
.  We   will   not   sell   broad   public   export   features   before

16
00:00:57.340 --> 00:00:59.800
  the   first   gate   is   stable .  <break time="600ms" />

 That   is   the  

17
00:00:59.800 --> 00:01:04.550
